Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管今天還是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望與大家共同幸福下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上這件果然是明智的選擇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:51.75,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,700)\blur3\pos(959,107)}歡迎來到鴨川！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 在半路上 碰到一位溺水的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在問你這身裝扮是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 住 住 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為回到海灘之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服跟褲子都不知道跑去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過老師請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無論何時都有攜帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既 然 有 的 話 就給我穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛有來自消防署的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你救起的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎平安地醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓 雖然有點突然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要幾點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空時來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社長吵著不管如何就是非妳不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要當學生會長的練習對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動服社還是一樣忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美智也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社員召集中喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你今天沒穿制服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那個在上學的途中搞丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人有夠誇張的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都還是高中生喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回答不了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（好了換手～）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棒極了 超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然穿制服的前輩也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這身也別有一番風味…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭部有效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘拜下風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我大賽前得到一場很好的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下你是選擇學生會或者劍道社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能圓圈地畫上句號了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且也是個社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待著您的三連霸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,團隊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京乃圓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你掉的東西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹嘛呢 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動服社終於出現新人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎麼回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多半年沒見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫停 暫停 暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正值青春的女高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得跟這無關吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有些話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要動！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓 喜歡鴨川嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算一輩子活在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎這樣問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生了什麼 馬上聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中泉洋子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會一直站在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認為若是你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能融洽地相處下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特意送制服過來的熱心腸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救援用途的這件泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是制服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務時有義務一直穿著這件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意識水準好高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來還想稱你同志的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同志是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有同樣志向 一起前進的夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在不用這種說法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家老姐喜歡這種名詞 一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個好字眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要成為我的同志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有什麼困擾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百分百會成為你的幫手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這條件不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼作為同志的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fin E Ld Si Laffinty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像外國人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫蘭就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是京乃圓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 終於變成兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼事不疑遲 同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有件很困擾的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼事我都會做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會駕駛機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起德・梅托里奧更深藍更耀眼的這顆星球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是我們要追求的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要做的就只有一件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equality那些傢伙可能藏在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(599,53)\fs42}Equality為拉丁文中的平等之意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將ORBIT調整為隨時能上的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(629,53)\fs42}ORBIT為拉丁文中的軌道之意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘖 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞雷 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候換成基利烏斯在指揮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這顆星球 看上去像是死過一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由理加納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然浮在海面上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移動過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移動？ 這個是船？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓 我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 剛剛有回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓圓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐上機器人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩的堂妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前有看過這個東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼…剛才的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德・梅托里奧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍一台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷前方七千公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各艦準備迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前跟這個機體有過約定才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論任何時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為同志的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同志…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人堅信這個機體具有強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equality命令我守護這個機體和你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我～們～來～自～宇～宙～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是不斷進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到站在那邊的管家先生說停為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊索…是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只會踩腳踏車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操控全部由我這邊做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要待在裡面就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是拒絕你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭會感到困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候來到鴨川啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼鴨川的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還完全不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答就只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颯太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在剛才起飛的機體中…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處於相當興奮的狀態中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要將聲音放出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之告訴她全部都由我們這邊操控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼都不要驚慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別像某人一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筆直地飛向這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算撞上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好戲現在才要上映呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像變成 很不得了的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能開動它就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這種觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又怎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇啊啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然擊破了亞空力場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…傳說中的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,VOX！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的劍道也不差啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要選的話 照我的步調上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓圈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 完了完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.07,0:23:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 要去吃什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三河燒？鴨川湯？房總燒烤也挺好吃的喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛妻便當就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是愛妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概不是吧 應該是說絕對不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 總之先叫個大叔努力做東西給我們吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 剛剛的聲音是誰
